Steps for datanode:
0. change host name to hadoopX ( vi /etc/hostname)
1. install git 
    sudo apt-get install git
    git clone https://github.com/nkhuyu/hadoopSetup
2. cd hadoopSetup
3. run ubuntu setup script
    sh ubuntuSetup.sh
4. ssh hduser@hadoopX
    sudo apt-get install git
    git clone https://github.com/nkhuyu/hadoopSetup
5. run datanode script
    sh datanode.sh
